{"article_id":"h3f0Ok9RczqzNSbz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Democrat Nancy Pelosi vowed on Thursday to retake the speakership of the U.S. House of Representatives","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"even as a string of critics within her party have said","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"they will oppose her bid .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"\" I intend to win the speakership with Democratic votes . ...","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"I have overwhelming support in my caucus","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"to be speaker of the House , \"","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"Pelosi , a liberal from San Francisco , said at a news conference .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"\" I happen to think","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that at this point , I ' m the best person for that . \"","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Democrats won control of the House of Representatives in congressional elections on Nov. 6 ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"while Republicans held their majority in the Senate .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Pelosi ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"who has led Democrats in the House for 16 years ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"wants to reclaim the top job of speaker","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"she held from 2007 to 2011 ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"when she was the first woman in that post .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"The House speaker is next in the line of presidential succession after the vice president .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"A small but vocal group of Democrats has argued","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that the 78-year-old Pelosi should step aside","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and allow change ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"she has not encouraged a younger generation of Democrats to move into leadership positions .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Pelosi is unpopular with many voters","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"and has become a punching bag for Republicans .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Some Democratic candidates","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"who won swing districts this month","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"made campaign pledges","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"to oppose Pelosi as speaker .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"Pelosi ' s critics say","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"such pledges opened the door to victory .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Pelosi ' s backers say","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"the former speaker has the experience","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"needed to challenge President Donald Trump","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"and has offered a legislative agenda","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"that includes Democratic goals","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"such as raising the federal minimum wage","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"and investing in climate-friendly infrastructure .","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"She is also a prodigious fundraiser , a tireless campaigner","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"and has a record","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"that includes passage of the Affordable Care Act ,","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"also known as Obamacare ,","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"when she was last speaker .","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"Protecting that law from repeated attacks by Republicans was a top issue for Democrats in their successful campaign for the House .","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"While Pelosi still has more support as leader than anyone else inside the Democratic caucus ,","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"which will pick its candidate for speaker on Nov. 28 ,","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"she might not have enough","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"to get the 218 votes","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"she would need","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"when the full House ,","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"including Republicans ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"votes on Jan. 3 .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Seventeen Democrats have signed a letter","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"pledging not to back Pelosi during the House floor vote ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Democratic aides said .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Asked about the letter ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"Pelosi told reporters","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"they should ask the signatories ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"14","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"of whom","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"she said","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"were men ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"what their motivations were .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"No challenger has emerged to Pelosi ,","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"although Representative Marcia Fudge , a former head of the Congressional Black Caucus , has told some media outlets","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"she is considering a bid .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"Fudge , 66 , a liberal from northeastern Ohio , supported Representative Tim Ryan ' s failed bid in 2016","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"to unseat Pelosi as Democratic leader .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Fudge told the HuffPost on Thursday","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"that some people oppose Pelosi","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"because they see her as an elitist ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"\" and I think","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to some degree she is . \"","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Representative Kathleen Rice of New York , another Pelosi critic , told reporters","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"that Pelosi ' s opposition in the Democratic caucus was \" north of 25 \" people","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"and \" once we are able to show","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"the leader can not get to 218 votes ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"whether it ' s Marcia","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"( Fudge )","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"or others ,","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"( people ) are going to throw their hat in the ring . \"","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Even some of Pelosi ' s supporters acknowledged a bottled-up desire for change among Democrats after many years with Pelosi at the helm .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"\" I ' m supporting Nancy","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"because no one is more skilled","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"and has earned it , \"","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"said Representative Gerald Connolly of Virginia .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"\" Having said that ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"there ' s a huge desire","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"that ' s quite understandable for change . \"","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"House Minority Leader Nancy Pelosi","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"( D-CA )","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"speaks during her weekly news conference on Capitol Hill in Washington , U.S. , November 15 , 2018 .","depth":5},{"id":92,"text":"/Yuri Gripas","depth":4},{"id":93,"text":"Others asked","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"how the party could turn on Pelosi after last week ' s House wins .","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"\" We just won more victories than at any point since Watergate with Nancy Pelosi as our leader , \"","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"said Jesse Ferguson , a Democratic strategist and former spokesman for Hillary Clinton .","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"Doug Heye , a Republican strategist","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"who launched a \" Fire Pelosi \" campaign in 2010","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"when he was with the Republican National Committee ,","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"pent-up frustration among Democratic members for a path to party leadership was legitimate","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"- but that it would be \" foolish \" for them to oust Pelosi in the speaker ' s race .","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"\" When I was at the RNC","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"we didn ' t launch a \" Fire Pelosi \" campaign","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"because she was ineffective .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"It was because she was effective , \"","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"Heye said in an interview .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":215,"left":0,"right":214,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":214,"left":195,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":150,"right":194